0.2.0

- add document -> text decoder api, and a bunch of decoders for common
  document types on unix systems (sorry windows users, you have to
  define your own decoders from scratch)

- track document md5 sums to determine if the source has changed and
  raise an easily catchable error in this case (see qa.rs)

- actually enforce open document limits

- implement document removal

0.1.0

- initial release
